### GET courses filtered by department and semester
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Courses?$filter=department_code eq 'CSE' and semester eq 2

### GET students with CGPA above 8.0
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Students?$filter=cgpa gt 8.0

### POST new student enrollment
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Enrollments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_ID": "s2222222-0000-0000-0000-000000000005",
  "course_code": "MB201",
  "enrollmentDate": "2024-06-01",
  "status": "Enrolled",
  "attendancePercent": 0.00
}

### GET all enrollments for a specific student
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Enrollments?$filter=student_ID eq 's2222222-0000-0000-0000-000000000001'

### GET courses where seats are available
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Courses?$filter=currentEnrolled lt maxStudents

### PATCH enrollment to add grade
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Enrollments(student_ID='s2222222-0000-0000-0000-000000000001',course_code='CS201')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grade": "A",
  "gradePoints": 4.00,
  "status": "Completed"
}